description: Litium AB engages in the provision of information technology services. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2016-05-31. The firm focuses on products and cloud-based services that are used in finance and sales. The firm develops and sells e-commerce platforms that are integrated to manage issues related to marketing, sales and product management. The products are used in both the business-to-business (B2B) and the business-to-consumer (B2C) segments. The Company’s customers are retail and e-commerce pure players.
name: Litium AB
